              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>
 in England.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_breast_screening_unit">Breast Screening Units</xref>
 are responsible for the delivery of 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nhs_breast_screening_programme">NHS Breast Screening Programmes</xref>
 locally to a defined population.        </p>
      <p>
